{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"亲爱的人民中国","authors":["苏菲亚·贝迦姆"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":3,"day":13}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的人民中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏菲亚·贝迦姆［印度］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1949年10月1日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛泽东主席在天安门城楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严宣告新中国的诞生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！那就是你——人民中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义制度带来解放生产力的神奇力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迅速地挣脱了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥饿和愚昧的桎梏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！那就是你——人民中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女平等，没有种族歧视，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处尊重人的权利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建立了没有剥削的社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！那就是你——人民中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行空前的经济改革，社会面貌日新月异，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发展中国家的榜样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向往的安谧的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！那就是你——人民中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上存在两种制度的对立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球充斥动乱、紧张、恐惧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与发展中国家站在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放出一群和平的白鸽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！那就是你——人民中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白开元　译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}